msgid ""
"If you are outside the US, we recommend NOWPayments (lowest fees, direct to "
"your wallet). If you are in the US, Stripe Crypto is also an option. You can"
" enable multiple services and let your visitors choose!"
msgstr ""
"Má tá tú taobh amuigh den Stáit Aontaithe, molaimid NOWPayments (caighdeán "
"is íochtair, díreach chuig do stór). Má tá tú sna Stáit Aontaithe, tá Stripe"
" Crypto freisin mar rogha. Is féidir leat seirbhísí iomlán a ghníomhachtú "
"agus d'úinéirí a ligean do rogha a dhéanamh!"

