msgid ""
"Stripe Crypto payments (USDC) are ONLY available for US-based businesses. If"
" you are outside the US, Stripe will only accept credit card payments to "
"your Stripe balance (not directly to crypto)."
msgstr ""
"Tá na híocaíochtaí Crypto Stripe (USDC) ar fáil NÓS amháin do ghnóthaí atá "
"leaganaithe sa Mheiriceá. Má tá tú taobh thiar den Mheiriceá, glac Stripe "
"ach híocaíochtaí cárta creidmheasa go dtí do bhuaill Stripe (ní bhfaigheann "
"sé go díreach chuig crypto)."

msgid ""
"If you are in the US, you can use Stripe to receive crypto directly. If "
"outside, consider NOWPayments or CoinGate for direct crypto payouts."
msgstr ""
"Má tá tú sa Mheiriceá, is féidir leat Stripe a úsáid chun crypto a fháil go "
"díreach. Má tá tú taobh thiar, smaoinigh ar NOWPayments nó CoinGate le "
"haghaidh íocaíochtaí crypto díreach."

